Package: preprocS2
Title: preprocessing of Sentinel-2 data downloaded from various data hubs / produced from various atmospheric correction methods
Version: 1.5.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Jean-Baptiste", 
					    family = "Feret", 
					    email = "jb.feret@teledetection.fr", 
					    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
					    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0151-1334")))
Description: The package preprocS2 allows production of raster stack from Sentinel-2 directories, as well as cropping, production of cloud mask. 
	It can download from various hubs: Scihub and google cloud using the package Sen2R, and image subsets via google earth engine using the package rgee.
License: GPL (>= 3)
